{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_12_level_main_12-16_beg","storyGroup":"main_12","storySort":138,"storyDependence":"main_12_level_main_12-16_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"12-18","storyName":"晚安","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"戈尔丁在变形者集群的见证下死去。重伤的贝尔德也独自一人走向了生命的终结。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_12-16_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_12-16","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":21,"next":23,"characters":["戈尔丁","变形者集群","“戈尔丁”","贝尔德"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"dialog","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":6},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f8/Avg_bg_32_g3_school_indoor.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":7},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":10,"musicid":0},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"感谢你，变形者，你答应了我的恳求。","id":12,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",7]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"这不是什么棘手的愿望。","id":14,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"很巧，我们刚从一些更讨厌的事情中腾出手来。","id":16,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"教室，你最终还是邀请我们来到了这里。","id":18,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#4$1","focus":"m","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"合情合理，戈尔丁，你毕竟是一位老师，你始终都是这么认为的。","id":20,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",3]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我想，我今天会死在这里。","id":22,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"你还是做了这个决定。","id":24,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"莱托会伤心的。","id":26,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我必须要这么做。","id":28,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"你为什么如此纠结于这一点？","id":30,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"是啊，我为什么如此纠结于这一点？","id":32,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我放不下孩子们，我担心他们在这个时代中会找不到自己的去向，我放不下茉莉，她是个好姑娘，但她不明白如何保护自己。","id":34,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"当然，还有海蒂......但我辜负了她，我只愿她不要怨恨我。","id":36,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这大概很难吧，那么多人因我而死。","id":38,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我该承受这种怨恨。","id":40,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"戈尔丁，你知道，这种死亡无法改变任何事。","id":42,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"说实话，这让我们困惑......","id":44,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"在我们经历的漫长时光中，拥抱死亡的人并不鲜见，可每次目睹我们仍然会感到不解。","id":46,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"我们熟悉这些词汇，“牺牲”“忏悔”“愧疚”，也许还有别的。","id":48,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"最后的结局总是通向死亡。","id":50,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"很抱歉，在我们看来，这十分徒劳，死亡没什么意义，不值得迷恋。","id":52,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"死了就是死了而已。","id":54,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我知道，变形者，我很明白你说的这些话。","id":56,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"如果我想弥补那些死去的自救军战士，更好的选择或许是继续活下去，照顾那些受到了伤害的家庭，为他们尽一份力。","id":58,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"可是，我知道，我没法做到，我没办法面对......","id":60,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我很害怕。","id":62,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#10$1","focus":"m","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"变形者集群","text":"甚至死亡都比这种恐惧要轻松吗？","id":64,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",9]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"也许。","id":66,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",0]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我一直在后退......我以为只要避让开那些浪潮，我就仍能保住我的生活。","id":68,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"可是退到哪一步我们才会承认旧的生活已经崩溃？","id":70,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......退到哪一步才会承认旧的生活其实从未存在？","id":72,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我没有办法面对这些，我宁愿在还未彻底绝望之前死去。","id":74,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",6]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_647_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"变形者，给我个骗自己的机会吧。","id":76,"figure":["avg_npc_647_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_426_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":78},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":79},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":80},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_humanchange","volume":"1","id":81},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"background","id":84},{"type":"image","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xFrom":"-20","yFrom":"20","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleTo":"1.0","yScaleTo":"1.0","duration":"40","block":"false","id":86},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"您变成了我的样子，变形者。","id":89,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"别误会，戈尔丁，我们没有那么喜欢自己的工作。我们不会去欺骗那些你珍重的人。","id":90,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"我们只是，想要更好地体会你的感情。","id":91,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"这种感情确实很难理解，我们只能去感受。","id":92,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"你曾问过我该如何生活。","id":93,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"......我又怎么可能知道。","id":94,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但是，当我真正发现自己的无力的时候，放弃也是一种选择，不是吗？","id":95,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"莱托也曾说起过这个词，放弃。","id":96,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"不，不是放弃自己，随波逐流。","id":97,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"而是放弃生活本身。","id":98,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"你说，“放弃生活本身”。","id":99,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这些经历......无论是愉悦的，还是痛苦的，没必要紧攥着不放，对吧。","id":100,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"特别是，你发现自己走入了一座迷宫之中，而建筑迷宫墙壁的，正是这些经历。","id":101,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"这实在算不上抗争，这是懦弱者的选择。","id":102,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"但我......起码不会再次站在他们那边了，对吧。","id":103,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"戈尔丁","text":"我......已经很困了。","id":104,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"......","id":105,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“戈尔丁”","text":"晚安，戈尔丁。","id":106,"figure":["avg_npc_426_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":107},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":108},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":110},{"type":"image","id":111},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/87/Avg_bg_25_mini02_victoria_street_n.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":112},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":114},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":115,"musicid":1},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"唉。","id":117,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"没力气了。","id":119,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",5]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"也好，我确实已经......足够累了。","id":121,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"哼，最起码最后的日子里，格拉斯哥帮又团聚了。","id":123,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"......希望他们能安全离开。","id":125,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"贝尔德踉跄地走到一堵墙边，缓缓坐了下来，在背后的墙上拉出一道长长的血痕。","id":128},{"type":"text","text":"她的手已经开始麻木，她想要握起拳头，但是不太成功。","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"哈。","id":131,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"啧......死确实比我想象的还要疼一些。起码比在下巴上挨上汉娜一拳要疼。","id":133,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":134},{"type":"charslot","id":135},{"type":"text","text":"她转过头，身侧不远处，躺倒着一具尸体，瘦小而干瘪，看样子已经死了有些日子。","id":136},{"type":"text","text":"她突然发现，这具尸体有些面熟。","id":137},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"“下个院士”先生，原来你在这里。","id":139,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"charslot","id":141},{"type":"text","text":"这位胆怯的市民面前躺着一个肉罐头，已经被吃得干干净净。","id":142},{"type":"text","text":"贝尔德眨了眨眼睛，似乎这个可怜人的身侧有些奇怪的东西。从墙上，到地上......一些黑色的曲线？","id":143},{"type":"text","text":"是一些文字，一些图样。","id":144},{"type":"text","text":"贝尔德这时才发现，他又捡了一支笔，一支破破烂烂的炭笔，远不及他的宝贝钢笔体面。","id":145},{"type":"text","text":"她摸了摸自己的口袋。本属于纹章学家的装饰精美的钢笔仍在她手边。可惜麦克拉伦没认真读这支华丽钢笔最后写下的那些文字。","id":146},{"type":"text","text":"她艰难地拖着自己的身躯，往那些墙上文字的方向挪了挪，仔细辨认着这些细小的字迹。","id":147},{"type":"text","text":"她笑了，忍不住咳嗽了起来。","id":148},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"一篇申请皇家科学院院士头衔的纹章学论文？","id":150,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"先生，你最后写下的就是这些东西？","id":152,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"这毫无用处。","id":154,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",8]},{"type":"dialog","id":155},{"type":"charslot","id":156},{"type":"text","text":"贝尔德跳过墙上那些大段大段让人不明就里的考证与阐释。","id":157},{"type":"text","text":"这篇论文没有结尾，一片空白之后，这位先生愤怒地写道，自己忘记了某些重要资料的内容。","id":158},{"type":"text","text":"他应该是绝望了，停了好一会儿，笔迹淡了几分。","id":159},{"type":"text","text":"在某个时刻，这位胆怯的市民开始书写起自己的愿望。","id":160},{"type":"dialog","id":161},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":162},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望《阿什沃思家族考》马上出现在我的手边。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":164},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望编辑们真正明白我工作的意义，并同意提高我的稿费。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"26","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":165},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望老师别生我的气，那些只是学术争论，我仍然尊敬他。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":166},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“好吧，如果有机会，我愿意放弃学术争论，再喝一次他泡的茶。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":167},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我还是很饿，想吃街角的那家炸鳞肉。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":168},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望简没有忘了我，我爱她，我仍像分开前一样爱她。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":169},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我是个混蛋，我希望拳馆的那些孩子没事。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":170},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我想喝三百万桶威士忌。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":171},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":172},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“萨朗姑姑，我想念你，我长大以后成了个坏孩子，对不起。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":173},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“该死的。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":174},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“该死的，谁来实现我的愿望？我已经竭尽所能地祈祷了，向那些所有我知道和不知道的存在。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":175},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“如果现在那鼓吹律法的黎博利修士出现在我面前，我一定揍他一顿。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":176},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“好吧，好吧。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":177},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望所有人都能实现他们的愿望，所有人都幸福快乐，所有人都能平安健康，所有人都能过上真正美好的生活，每一个人。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":178},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望再没有人受苦，再没有人被折磨，大家都应该笑，眼泪从这片大地上消失。饿肚子也消失。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":179},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望这一切没有白费。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":180},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我希望这一切——”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":181},{"type":"subtitle","text":"一道长长的划痕后，笔迹在这里消失。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":182},{"type":"subtitle","id":183},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"......","id":186,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",1]},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"好吧，这就是最后了。","id":188,"figure":["avg_npc_863_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"charslot","id":190},{"type":"text","text":"贝尔德艰难地抬起手，这支钢笔快干了，她试了好几次才留下一道短短的黑色墨迹。","id":191},{"type":"dialog","id":192},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":193},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.6","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.7","block":"true","id":194},{"type":"subtitle","text":"“我也希望。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":195},{"type":"subtitle","id":196},{"type":"dialog","id":197},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":199},{"type":"character","id":200},{"type":"image","id":201}],"characters":["戈尔丁","变形者集群","“戈尔丁”","贝尔德"]}